<html>
    <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Submissions</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300..700;1,300..700&family=Noto+Sans:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
</head>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: black;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;

        

        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        
    }
    .page-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;   
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 80px;
}


.stack-section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 30px;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 100px auto;
  color: white;
  font-family: Cinzel;
  font-style: italic;
}

.box {
  padding: 40px;
  background: #1f0631;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 12px;


  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards;
}

/* Stagger effect */
.box:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.box:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
.box:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
.box:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 1.1s; }

@keyframes fadeUp {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}


.hero-header {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: 60px;
}

.header-box {
  width: 70%;
  max-width: 800px;
  padding: 80px 40px;

  background-image: url("/images/Sban.png"); 
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;

  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 10px rgba(241, 44, 234, 0.6);

  text-align: center;

  /* Animation start state */
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease forwards;
}

.header-box::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
    rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)
  );
}
.header-box h1 {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  font-style: italic;
  font-size: 3.2rem;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  color: white;
}


@keyframes fadeInUp {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}


.submission-pdf {
  width: 85%;
  margin: 100px auto;
}

.submission-pdf iframe {
  border: none;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}
 </style>


<body>

<header class="hero-header">
  <div class="header-box">
    <h1>STRATEGY SUBMISSIONS</h1>
  </div>
</header>


  </div>

<section class="stack-section">
  <div class="box">
    <p>Iteron is an open tournament.Any strategy that follows the interface contract can compete </p>

  </div>
  <div class="box">
    <p>Read the rules,<br> write your code,<br>
         and submit.
         </p>
  </div>
  
  

<section class="submission-pdf">
  <iframe 
    src="/rulebook.pdf"
    width="100%" 
    height="900px">
  </iframe>
</section>

</body>
</html>
